messageBody:
The polls set up last February regarding members' use of the Read
Alphabet will close on Sept. 11, 2005. If you have not yet answered
the poll, and you would like to, get a move on. Time's running out.

If anyone has a poll they want to propose, don't be bashful. I
sometimes think that lurking has been raised to a fine art in this group.

Paige
